    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_02-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "――今回のCM撮影に臨む際に意識したこと、ですか",
      "startTime": 2.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_02-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "そうですね……今回の撮影は\n大切な人のことを考えて臨みました",
      "startTime": 10.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 13.8
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_02-rui003.m4a",
      "text": "といっても、恋愛的な意味ではないんですけど",
      "startTime": 13.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_02-rui004.m4a",
      "text": "バレンタインにチョコレートを渡す人は、好きな人や\n友達、家族……いろいろな人がいると思います",
      "startTime": 21.0333353679,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 25.6666687012
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_02-rui005.m4a",
      "text": "ですが、大切な人に想いを伝えるという点は\n共通していると思うんです",
      "startTime": 30.3000020345,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 32.4000020345
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_02-rui006.m4a",
      "text": "なので、大切なメンバーのこと、支えてくれる\nファンのみなさんのことを意識しました",
      "startTime": 36.3666687012,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_02-rui007.m4a",
      "text": "私の気持ちが、画面を通して少しでも伝わったら\nとても嬉しいです",
      "startTime": 43.1333353679,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 44.9333353679
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（瑠依……凄く満足そうだな）\n（うまくいって良かった）",
      "startTime": 48.3666687012,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "3d_toffice_noon",
      "startTime": 51.4333353679
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "瑠依、お疲れ様",
      "startTime": 53.3000020345,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_02-rui008.m4a",
      "text": "は、はい。お疲れ様です",
      "startTime": 55.2333353679,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "瑠依の演技、スタッフのみなさんにも好評だったよ\n放送が楽しみだな",
      "startTime": 62.0666687012,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_02-rui009.m4a",
      "text": "あはは、そ、そうですね",
      "startTime": 64.2666687012,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "そういえば、今日は現場でスタッフさんと\n話し込んでたな。どんな話をしてたんだ？",
      "startTime": 70.0666687012,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_02-rui010.m4a",
      "text": "バレンタインにまつわる体験談を聞いていたんです",
      "startTime": 73.9000020345,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "なるほどな、現場でも勉強してたのか",
      "startTime": 77.3666687012,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_02-rui011.m4a",
      "text": "はい、沢山学びがありました\n学びが、あったんですけど",
      "startTime": 85.1666687012,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_02-rui012.m4a",
      "text": "あの、ですね……",
      "startTime": 88.6333353679,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_02-rui013.m4a",
      "text": "スタッフさんからいろんなお話を聞いた上で\n撮影をしたら……",
      "startTime": 93.3666687012,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_02-rui014.m4a",
      "text": "バレンタインの重要性が、ちょっとだけ\n分かったかも、と言いますか",
      "startTime": 98.3666687012,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "ん……？　どうしたんだ、そんなもじもじして",
      "startTime": 101.5333353679,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_02-rui015.m4a",
      "text": "その、本当は当日にお渡しする予定だったんです。でも\nなんだかいろいろと余計なことを考えちゃって……",
      "startTime": 111.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_02-rui016.m4a",
      "text": "当日に渡したら、『そういう』意味だと\n誤解されてしまうような気がして……！",
      "startTime": 117.2666687012,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_02-rui017.m4a",
      "text": "あ、いえ、杞憂だなって分かってるんですよ？",
      "startTime": 119.6333353679,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_02-rui018.m4a",
      "text": "あくまで、早めに渡した方がその、なんの問題もなく\n気持ち良くことが済むかなと思いまして……！",
      "startTime": 127.0666687012,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-call-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5599.9999999999945,
          "startTime": 132.6666687012
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_02-rui019.m4a",
      "text": "ですから、{user}さん！\nこれを――",
      "startTime": 132.1000020345,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "おっと、すまない\n電話は……橋本さん？",
      "startTime": 135.266667684,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3666.6656493000005,
          "startTime": 138.9333333333
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-end-01.m4a",
          "delay": 11093.332316000016,
          "startTime": 146.36
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "もしもし……そうか、分かった\n今から行くから、十五分くらいで着くよ",
      "startTime": 143.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "申し訳ない。現場でちょっとトラブルがあって……ん？\n瑠依、どうしたんだ？　ぽかんとして……",
      "startTime": 151.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_02-rui020.m4a",
      "text": "いえ、その……なんでもありません\nそれより、早く行った方がいいんじゃないですか？",
      "startTime": 159.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_02-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "（瑠依……どうしたんだろう？）",
      "startTime": 163.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――バレンタイン数日前",
      "startTime": 167.3666666667,
      "sfxList": [
